<h4>榴莲键盘</h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1376336" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/69a1aa0a977d4cce9b13b71e6061d328.png" alt="" width="777" height="474" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/69a1aa0a977d4cce9b13b71e6061d328.png 777w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/69a1aa0a977d4cce9b13b71e6061d328-360x220.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/69a1aa0a977d4cce9b13b71e6061d328-768x469.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 777px) 100vw, 777px" /></p>
<p>近日，一款配有「榴莲」键帽的键盘在网上引起热议。有报道称，这款键盘出自深圳「键鼠狂人」陆航之手，是针对双 11 的创意产品。值得指出的是，虽然这款键盘是机械键盘，但键帽上却没有刻上字母。</p>
<p>网友：「跪榴莲还是键盘？现在终于没有选择困难了！」「这设计，男同胞坑男同胞啊。」</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357580" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed.png" alt="" width="1029" height="165" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-360x58.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-768x123.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-1024x164.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4>「这是我看到的音乐」</h4>
<p><iframe src="https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=b3165z0d6ze" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" data-mce-fragment="1"></iframe></p>
<p>（<a href="https://v.qq.com/x/page/b3165z0d6ze.html">腾讯视频</a>）</p>
<p>以色列动画师 <a href="http://www.michalevy.com/">Michal Levy</a> 是能体验「联觉」的人，这意味着她在体验一种感知刺激的时候，也会触发另一种感知。</p>
<p>以 Levy 为例，她在听到声音/音乐时，同时会获得视觉感知。作为一位动画师，Levy 将自己在聆听音乐《Giant Steps》时的视觉体验动画化，让更多人能看到她所看到的音乐。</p>